Known Markers Example

known_markers_small

Format

An object of class grouped_df (inherits from tbl_df, tbl, data.frame) with 28 rows and 14 columns.

See also

Other Minimal Example Data: all_markers_small, cellranger_small, indrops_small, seurat_small
